<h1>Job matching <br />With personality.</h1>
<p>FitIn is a pre-screening culture match tool for employers to find the right candidates the first time.</p>
<h3>Currently in Beta Testing.</h3>
<h3>Origin Story:</h3>
<p>We had a problem fitting in at work. We were tired of the hassle involved in applying, interviewing, and eventually getting hired at jobs where we didn't fit in. We created a tool that visually shows the Ethical, Social, and Professional matches between companies and job seekers.</p>
<p>We are giving everyone ESP.</p>
<p>FitIn gives you more time to do the things that matter.</p>
